<DOCHDR>
http://www.lead-inst.org:80/wash_times/pruden.2-26.html 204.71.237.80 19970210123215 text/html 5436
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 12:33:01 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 26-Feb-96 05:56:32 GMT
