<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist Donald Devine</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Donald Devine</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-devine.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>






<a href="/townhall/columnists/devine.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
<UL>
<li>January 17, 1997 <a href="/conservative/columnists/dev011797.html">Will Election Shock Alter GOP'S Course?</a>
<li>August 10, 1996 <a href="/conservative/columnists/devi0810.html">Betting On Dole</a>
<li>June 26, 1996 <a href="/conservative/columnists/devi0626.html">Momentous Welfare Decision</a>
<li>June 23, 1996 <a href="/conservative/columnists/devi0623.html">Equal Opportunity for the GOP</a>
<li>May 14, 1996  <a href="/conservative/columnists/devi0513.html">Regarding the Abortion Plank</a>
<li>May 9, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/devine/devi050896.html">Get Political, GOP</a>
<li>May 9, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/devine/devi050996.html">Real Campaign Reform</a>
<li>May 7, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/devine/devi050796.html">The Right's Confused But the Left is Dead</a>
<li>February 20, 1996 <a href="/conservative/columnists/devi0219.html">The Myth of the GOP Electoral Lock</A>
<li>February 20, 1996 <a href="/conservative/columnists/devi0220.html">What Now?</a>
