http://www.lead-inst.org:80/heritage/commentary/op-ef32.html 204.71.237.80 19970217110524 text/html 4737
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 11:06:21 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 13-Jan-97 15:39:22 GMT
