http://www.lead-inst.org:80/wash_times/fields.6-30.html 204.71.237.80 19970217124019 text/html 6094
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 12:41:17 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 25-Jun-96 15:14:17 GMT
Content-length: 5910
