<head>
<title>Columnist Michael Fumento</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Michael Fumento</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-fumento.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>






<a href="/townhall/columnists/fumento.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
<UL>
<li>January 22, 1997 <a href="/townhall/columnists/fumento/fume012297.html">Crime Rate Decline Calls for Introspection--and Caution</a>
<li>January 8, 1997 <a href="/townhall/columnists/fumento/fume010897.html">Cops Pay the Price for New Gun Law</a>
<li>December 19, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/fumento/fume121996.html">Greens Still Trying to Salvage Their Alar-Stained Reputation</a>
<li>December 11, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/fumento/fume121196.html">Women's Magazines Are Pink Propaganda</a>
