<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Thomas Schatz</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-schatz.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>






